A1=Matrix([[3, -1], [-1, 3]])
t=var('t')
image=Graphics()
circle_pos=parametric_plot((cos(t), sin(t)),(t,0,2*pi))
image +=circle_pos
for th in range(80):
        angle=(2*pi*th)/80
        r=matrix([[cos(angle),-sin(angle)],[sin(angle),cos(angle)]])
        image += parametric_plot(r * vector([t,0]),(t,0,1),color="black")
        image += parametric_plot(A1 * r * vector([t,0])+r*vector([1,0]),(t,0,1),color="purple")
eigenvectors = A1.eigenvectors_right()
eigenvectors #[(4,[(1,-1)],1),(2,[(1,1)],1)]
eigenvalue=4
eigenvector=vector([1,1])
eigenvalue_1=2
eigenvector_1=vector([1,-1])
image += parametric_plot(t*eigenvector, (t, -2, 2), color='red',thickness=2)
image += parametric_plot(t*eigenvector_1, (t, -2, 2), color='red',thickness=2)
image.show()

image=Graphics()
A3 = Matrix([[1/2, 3/2], [0, -1]])
t=var('t')
circle_pos=parametric_plot((cos(t), sin(t)),(t,0,2*pi))
image +=circle_pos
th=var("th")
for th in range(80):
        angle=(2*pi*th)/80
        r=matrix([[cos(angle),-sin(angle)],[sin(angle),cos(angle)]])
        image += parametric_plot(r * vector([t,0]),(t,0,1),color="black")
        image += parametric_plot(A3 * r * vector([t,0])+r*vector([1,0]),(t,0,1),color="purple")
eigenvectors = A3.eigenvectors_right()       
eigenvectors #[(1/2,[(1,0)],1),(-1,[(1,-1)],1)]
eigenvalue=1/2
eigenvector=vector([1,-1])
eigenvalue_1=-1
eigenvector_1=vector([1,0])
image += parametric_plot(t*eigenvector, (t, -2, 2), color='red',thickness=2)
image += parametric_plot(t*eigenvector_1, (t, -2, 2), color='red',thickness=2)
image.show()

        image += parametric_plot(r * vector([t,0]),(t,0,1),color="black")
